snippet.title: Evercade - Team17 Collection 1 Trailer - AMIGA GAMES!
snippet.description:
Amiga comes to Evercade with 10 great games from legendary British Publisher Team17. Legal Amiga emulation for the first time on a handheld device means that people can take these home computer favourites on the go!

Team17 Collection 1 is Compatible with all Evercade systems running Firmware version 3.0.X or above. Please update your system by updating on your console or by visiting evercade.co.uk/support for more information.

Available May 2023
Pre-order from March 17th 2023

Find out more: https://evercade.co.uk/cartridges/team17-collection-1-amiga/

Full Games List:
Alien Breed Special Edition ‘92
Alien Breed II
Alien Breed Tower Assault
Arcade Pool
ATR: All Terrain Racing
Body Blows
Full Contact
Kingpin: Arcade Sports Series Bowling
Project X: Special Edition ‘93
Qwak
